Rating: 4
I can't believe I haven't reviewed this recipe! This will be my 4th Thanksgiving making it. It's my absolute go to cranberry recipe. If you have not made this.... DO! Well balanced flavors, great texture, and bouquet. Further more it makes well ahead, but it is quick enough to do same day.

