Rating: 4
I was a little apprehensive about leaving the skin on the orange, but I was not disappointed! The slight bitterness of the orange peel combined with the sweetness of the suger and the tartness of the cranberry was amazing! Easy to make and very good!

Rating: 3
The liquid portion of this dish tastes amazing. I just doubled the cranberry and liquid part, and added it to the orange. The only other thing I would reccomend is to cut the oranges small.